## Adding it to an iPhone home screen

1. Open the deployed URL in **Safari** on the iPhone.
2. Tap the **Share** button.
3. Tap **Add to Home Screen**.

## Adding another person later

Edit the `USERS` array in `src/users.ts`, and add the name to the
`isKnownUser` list in `firestore.rules`, then redeploy.
